
& maneuvering_ace
 
 >> Help: Maneuvering Ace (Advantage)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Type 'turnmode tight' to toggle this advantage on.
 Type 'turnmode normal' to toggle this advantage off.
 
 Better BTH on lateral movements in non-VTOL units
 
 Result: You can move easier laterally in non-VTOL units, and you can change
 your turning style to make sharper turns - at the cost of losing more speed
 whilst doing so.
 
 For a detailed look at this advantage, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
